content:
I have a list of outdoor activities in a JSON format as shown below:
{
  "activities": [
    {
      "name": "Hiking",
      "difficulty": "moderate",
      "duration": "3-4 hours",
      "equipment": "hiking boots, water bottle, sunscreen",
      "location": "mountain trail"
    },
    {
      "name": "Kayaking",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "duration": "2-3 hours",
      "equipment": "life jacket, paddle, waterproof bag",
      "location": "lake or river"
    },
    {
      "name": "Rock Climbing",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "duration": "4-5 hours",
      "equipment": "climbing shoes, harness, chalk bag",
      "location": "rocky cliff"
    },
    {
      "name": "Biking",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "duration": "2-3 hours",
      "equipment": "bicycle, helmet, water bottle",
      "location": "bike trail"
    }
  ]
}
Can you suggest a random outdoor activity from the above list? Please specify the name of the activity, its difficulty level, duration, required equipment, and preferred location.
